WEBVTT

29:08.440 --> 29:09.390 line:80%
Is it all for me?

29:10.320 --> 29:12.800 line:80%
For those who suffered at the hands
of the Qingfeng Stronghold bandits

29:12.800 --> 29:14.110 line:80%
and lost family members,

29:14.110 --> 29:15.910 line:80%
the government has issued
consolation money.
